address2: 3rd floor Ballard Estate J. N. Heredia Marg
longBusinessSummary: Foods and Inns Limited engages in the manufacture and sale of various processed tropical fruits and vegetables pulps, purees, spices, spray dried powders, frozen foods, and other value-additive foods in India and internationally. The company offers aseptic and retort purees and concentrates of mango, guava, banana, tomato, grape, papaya, tamarind, turmeric, chili, ginger, garlic, and pomegranate. It also provides frozen IQF, pulper, spiralizer, and dicer products made from beetroot, zucchini, butternut squash, strawberry, pomegranate, watermelon, sweet potato, mango, blackberry, and other fruits and vegetables, as well as flat bread and Indian snacks. In addition, the company offers spray dying powders of lemon, tomato, cheese, beetroot, mango, caramel, honey, tamarind, and others; and industrial processor spices made from red chili, turmeric, curry, coriander, cumin, black pepper, garlic, ginger, and other whole ground blends, as well as garam masala. It offers its products under Madhu, Kusum, and Greentop brands. The company was incorporated in 1967 and is based in Mumbai, India.
